"Barely Political,"

00:00:03.710 --> 00:00:05.370
and of course, BJ Novak.

00:00:07.945 --> 00:00:09.070
TODD WOMACK: Hi, everybody.

00:00:09.070 --> 00:00:09.855
How are you guys doing?

00:00:09.855 --> 00:00:10.290
AUDIENCE: Great.

00:00:10.290 --> 00:00:12.623
TODD WOMACK: How about another
hand for our friend who's

00:00:12.623 --> 00:00:13.232
