00:00:13.232 --> 00:00:14.065
BJ NOVAK: Thank you.

00:00:14.065 --> 00:00:16.780
TODD WOMACK: Look at that.

00:00:16.780 --> 00:00:17.440
All right.

00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:17.970
So, BJ.

00:00:17.970 --> 00:00:18.595
BJ NOVAK: Yeah.

00:00:18.595 --> 00:00:20.820
TODD WOMACK: An
afternoon with BJ Novak.

