Look at all these
dedicated Googlers

00:00:22.490 --> 00:00:26.645
missing the Board of Directors
meeting just to see you.

00:00:26.645 --> 00:00:29.020
BJ NOVAK: I understand you
have a choice in presentations

00:00:29.020 --> 00:00:31.180
