This sound effect is part
of the story, by the way.

00:22:24.250 --> 00:22:25.666
TODD WOMACK:
Somebody's just going

00:22:25.666 --> 00:22:28.532
to complete the drywall
back there as we go.

00:22:28.532 --> 00:22:30.490
BJ NOVAK: So again, some
of these are 20 pages,

00:22:30.490 --> 00:22:32.490
and some of them
are half a page.

00:22:32.490 --> 00:22:34.922
This one is closer
to the latter.

00:22:34.922 --> 00:22:36.380
This is called,
"The Man Who Posted

00:22:36.380 --> 00:22:39.870
Pictures of Everything He Ate."

00:22:39.870 --> 00:22:43.220
"Once, there was a man
who posted pictures online

00:22:43.220 --> 00:22:46.210
of most of the things he ate.

00:22:46.210 --> 00:22:48.480
He put up pictures
of most of his meals

00:22:48.480 --> 00:22:52.220
and some of his snacks
with little captions.

00:22:52.220 --> 00:23:00.230
'Yum!' 'I made this myself.'
'Hits the spot.' 'Salty.' 'I'm

00:23:00.230 --> 00:23:06.150
going to regret this tomorrow.'
'Yum!' And plenty of times,

00:23:06.150 --> 00:23:09.030
most of the time, he simply
let the pictures speak

00:23:09.030 --> 00:23:10.840
for themselves.

00:23:10.840 --> 00:23:16.320
The 16, then 15, then
16, then 14 people

00:23:16.320 --> 00:23:21.280
who followed him made fun
of him for it mercilessly.

00:23:21.280 --> 00:23:24.790
'Why do you post pictures of
your food?' 'We don't give

00:23:24.790 --> 00:23:28.100
a [PAUSE] what you
ate.' " In the book,

00:23:28.100 --> 00:23:30.650
the swears are not bleeped out,
but this person in the thread

00:23:30.650 --> 00:23:31.600
bleeped it out.

00:23:31.600 --> 00:23:33.599
Just explaining.

00:23:33.599 --> 00:23:34.890
TODD WOMACK: I can verify that.

00:23:34.890 --> 00:23:37.730
BJ NOVAK: "The more they
teased him, the more he did it.

00:23:37.730 --> 00:23:41.360
And the more he did it,
the more they teased him.

00:23:41.360 --> 00:23:46.695
'Why do you always post pics
of your food?' He did it

00:23:46.695 --> 00:23:49.320
because it made him feel like he
was eating his meals with more

00:23:49.320 --> 00:23:50.940
people.

00:23:50.940 --> 00:23:56.050
It was the same reason
he liked the teasing."

00:23:56.050 --> 00:23:57.700
TODD WOMACK: Sad, sweet, funny.

